**Trigger:** User mentions `@execute-specflow`

**This rule loads the TDD-enforced implementation flow**

---

## Load Command

**Read:** `.fwdpro/pro-os/commands/flows/execute-specflow.md`

This flow command implements technical specifications with **mandatory TDD enforcement** and structured quality phases.

---

## When to Use This

✅ **Use `@execute-specflow` when:**
- Implementing from a technical spec
- Want TDD enforced (tests pass before shipping)
- Need bulletproof implementation quality
- Building features (not content/strategy)

❌ **Use `@execute` instead when:**
- Flexible implementation needed
- Content or campaign execution
- No strict TDD requirements

