## Key Principles

- **TDD Enforcement:** All tests must pass before completion (non-negotiable)
- **Three-Phase Workflow:** Pre-Flight → Execution → Post-Flight (MANDATORY QA phase)
- **Expert Integration:** Works best with Ada (or Denny for architecture)
- **Quality First:** `code-checklist.md` MUST be validated at end + all tests passing (no shipping without both)
